cs.DL, cs.IR, cs.HC, cs.SI, cs.CL 

The paper discusses a tool for analyzing and visualizing the intellectual histories of scientific fields through citation analysis. This falls under the sub-categories of digital libraries (cs.DL), information retrieval (cs.IR), human-computer interaction (cs.HC), social and information networks (cs.SI), and computational linguistics (cs.CL).
